        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "this year. The defence company's order backlog of £70bn is its biggest ever and includes new nuclear-powered submarines for the Australian and British navies. BAE is also restarting production of parts for the M777 howitzer, used to great effect by Ukraine against Russia.",
        "bbox": [
